Beat first 5 ingredients in medium bowl until stiff peaks form. Line each of 4 old-fashioned glasses with angel food cake round and sprinkle with 1/2 teaspoon rum, if desired. Drop scant 1 tablespoon jam on each; spread jam to edge of cake. Top with heaping tablespoon pineapple cubes, heaping tablespoon cream mixture, and 1 tablespoon coconut. Repeat layering. Garnish each trifle with fresh pineapple wedge.